      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK, so my cousin with our friend got one room with a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went for two weeks and we went to Czechoslovakia again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
