      "text": "Somebody was living there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to my-- and this was a widow with her children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the husband was killed for the-- the German killed him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
